  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387620/extras/6d0597437abbc1db75a9b4d179507fef.avif?t=1603180898\" width=648 height=324 /></span><br>Help Emran rescue his daughter (Aisha) who has been taken from his arms. You will join him in his journey through the castles and forests to meet the king.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Heartfelt story at the beginning to the end of game.<br><br></li><li>A beautiful world of animals, creatures and warriors.<br><br></li><li>Traditional 2D animation that brings creatures and characters to life.<br><br></li><li>Challenging gameplay that can be difficult but always fair.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387620/extras/dee38f1a236e029de95229916224b693.poster.avif?t=1603180898\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387620/extras/dee38f1a236e029de95229916224b693.webm?t=1603180898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387620/extras/dee38f1a236e029de95229916224b693.mp4?t=1603180898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>A collection of challenging traps, that the most skilled players can strive for.<br><br></li><li>The game has a beautifully authentic style that bridges the gap between yesterday and today. Design, art, and audio hearken back to the days of 8-bit, The systems of today also give Save Aisha modern touches, detailed animation, multilayered parallax backgrounds, and novel game design.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387620/extras/a5fb32ca98528ea7f10071749cc2d875.poster.avif?t=1603180898\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387620/extras/a5fb32ca98528ea7f10071749cc2d875.webm?t=1603180898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387620/extras/a5fb32ca98528ea7f10071749cc2d875.mp4?t=1603180898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Full Controller Support.<br><br></li><li>Multiple vibrant soundtracks by: Fabian - Of Far Different Nature, Juhani Junkala, Mega Pixel Music Lab, and Syncopika.<br><br></li><li>Multiple awesome traps animated and drawn by SAINT11.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387620/extras/ebe56a42a9119d7a23d4dc716bc859f3.poster.avif?t=1603180898\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387620/extras/ebe56a42a9119d7a23d4dc716bc859f3.webm?t=1603180898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387620/extras/ebe56a42a9119d7a23d4dc716bc859f3.mp4?t=1603180898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Awesome  enemy characters by Hugues Laborde, Openpixelproject, and Luiz Melo.<br><br></li><li>heartfelt story Drawings By Amany Alshayeb.<br><br></li><li>Amazing tilsets made by Luis Zuni, Openpixelproject, and CraftPix</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387620/extras/2cc31fbdf7c47a40fc816acafa3acb7b.poster.avif?t=1603180898\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387620/extras/2cc31fbdf7c47a40fc816acafa3acb7b.webm?t=1603180898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387620/extras/2cc31fbdf7c47a40fc816acafa3acb7b.mp4?t=1603180898\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
